              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="hero-sub" data-anim="fade-up" data-delay="260">
              Kami bantu <strong>UMKM &amp; Perusahaan</strong> Indonesia
              membangun Web App, Company Profile, hingga Sistem Kasir modern —
              cepat, clean, dan SEO-ready.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-cta-row" data-anim="fade-up" data-delay="360">
              <a
                href="https://wa.me/6285706193924?text=Halo%20SukaSuka.web,%20saya%20ingin%20konsultasi%20gratis."
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn btn-primary btn-lg magnetic-btn"
                aria-label="Konsultasi gratis via WhatsApp"
              >
                <span class="btn-inner">💬 Konsultasi Gratis</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="#paket"
                class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg magnetic-btn"
                aria-label="Lihat paket harga"
              >
                <span class="btn-inner">Lihat Paket →</span>
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-stats-comic" data-anim="fade-up" data-delay="460">
              <div class="hstat-item">
                <div class="hstat-label">Kepuasan Klien</div>
                <div class="hstat-bar-wrap">
                  <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div
                      class="progress-fill"
                      data-width="100"
                      style="width: 0%"
                    ></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hstat-val">
                  <span class="counter" data-target="100">0</span>%
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hstat-item">
                <div class="hstat-label">Respon Cepat</div>
                <div class="hstat-bar-wrap">
                  <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div
                      class="progress-fill fill-cyan"
                      data-width="95"
                      style="width: 0%"
                    ></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hstat-val">
                  &lt;<span class="counter" data-target="24">0</span>jam
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hstat-item">
                <div class="hstat-label">DP Awal</div>
                <div class="hstat-bar-wrap">
                  <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div
                      class="progress-fill fill-yellow"
                      data-width="50"
                      style="width: 0%"
                    ></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hstat-val">
                  <span class="counter" data-target="50">0</span>%
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="scroll-panel">
            <span
              class="font-display text-xs"
              style="letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase"
