            <div class="marquee-slide" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="mq-item">✦ MADRASAH ALIYAH TARBIYAH ISLAMIYAH</span
              ><span class="mq-sep">◆</span>
              <span class="mq-item">PT. REONCY INDO ABADI</span
              ><span class="mq-sep">◆</span>
              <span class="mq-item">✦ MADRASAH ALIYAH TARBIYAH ISLAMIYAH</span
